About Event
​Building a startup is definitely not a walk in the park, but we're going to walk in the park anyway!

​Join Platform Venture Studio to meet, walk, network, and discuss early-stage startup building.

​Places are limited so please request to join if you are interested.

​Who Should Come

​Startup founders (current and aspiring)

​Investors in early stage startups (funds, angels, family offices)

​Academics teaching and studying entrepreneurship

​Why You Should Come

​Discussion of id
